18 SCHEDULE I. Receipts and disbursements.
19 SCHEDULE II. Assets of the pension trust, listing investments as
20 to book value and current market value at the end of the fiscal
21 year.
22 SCHEDULE III. List of terminations, showing cause and amount
23 of refund.
